---
title: Pork and Pak Choi Rice with chilli and coriander
description: Pak choi is a popular ingredient in Chinese cuisine, but did you know it's actually a type of cabbage? It can be prepared in many ways, but is at its best when slightly softened with a bit of bite left, which is precisely how it is in this recipe.
